Source: halos-mdns-publisher
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Hat Labs Ltd <info@hatlabs.fi>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cargo, rustc, libssl-dev, pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/hatlabs/halos-mdns-publisher

Package: halos-mdns-publisher
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, avahi-daemon, avahi-utils
Recommends: docker.io | docker-ce
Conflicts: halos-mdns-publisher-container
Replaces: halos-mdns-publisher-container
Description: HaLOS mDNS subdomain publisher
 Native systemd service that advertises container subdomains via mDNS.
 Monitors Docker containers for the halos.subdomain label and uses
 avahi-publish to advertise the corresponding subdomains.
 .
 Features:
  - Monitors Docker for containers with halos.subdomain label
  - Publishes subdomains as <subdomain>.<hostname>.local
  - Automatic cleanup when containers stop
  - Graceful degradation if Docker is unavailable
